---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  locale="en"
  title="Cookie Notice | Hooosberg"
  description="Cookie and local storage notice for Hooosberg, including analytics consent choices."
  canonicalPath="/en/cookies"
>
  <section class="legal-page">
    <p class="hero-kicker">Legal</p>
    <h1>Cookie Notice</h1>
    <p class="legal-page__updated">Last updated: 2026-06-21</p>

    <p>
      hooosberg.com keeps tracking minimal. The website mainly uses browser local storage for language, theme, and analytics consent choices.
    </p>

    <h2>Essential preferences</h2>
    <p>
      Theme, language, and analytics consent choices may be stored in your browser so the site can respect your preferences.
    </p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      If Google Analytics is configured, the analytics script loads only after you accept analytics. It helps us understand traffic,
      content performance, and improvement priorities. If you decline, non-essential analytics does not load.
    </p>

    <h2>Changing your choice</h2>
    <p>
      You can clear site data for hooosberg.com in your browser, or run this in developer tools:
    </p>
    <pre><code>window.HooosbergAnalytics?.resetConsent()</code></pre>

    <h2>External platforms</h2>
    <p>
      Third-party links or embedded services may use cookies, logs, or analytics under their own policies.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
